@startuml
title Class Diagram Title

interface IFoo {
  + void method(); // public
}

abstract class Bar {
  + {static} String name;
  ~ Foo foo;
  # int x; // protected
  ~ int y; // default
  - void method(String string); // private
}

class Foo {
  ~ int x;
  ~ void methodA();
}

class Qoo {
  ~ Foo foo;
}

note right of Foo
  public : +
  protected : #
  default : ~
  private : -
  Foo는 Bar가 Aggregation한다.(Bar -o Foo)
  Foo는 Qoo가 Composition한다.(Qoo -* Foo)
  Foo는 IFOoo를 상속한다.(Foo -|> IFoo)
end note

note bottom of Bar
  void method(String string){
    return string;
  }
end note

Bar -o Foo
Qoo -*  Foo
Foo -|> IFoo
Bar ..> IFoo

@enduml